title: C&E TOOGOO Display Port to HDMI Converter with Audio Adapter
description: Brand new high quality GTMax Brand adapter.Connect your DisplayPort using HDMI cables with this adapter.Display Port v1.1 Compliant Enable high quality optional digital audio transmissionsEmbedded clock architecture to reduce EMI susceptibility. Support greater then AXGA (2048 x 1536) resolution at 24 bit color depths. Hot plug and un-plug detection as well as link status - failure detection Support reduced bandwidth transmission via direct drive over a 15 meter cable. Supports a minimum of 1080P resolution at 24bpp, 50/60 Hz at 15 meters. Support conversation from DisplayPort signal to DVI signal. 8 bit & 10 bit deep color. Connectors: DisplayPort Male to HDMI Female.UPC Code: 084331496336.
